# 📖 Chapter 10 – Image SEO

---

# 🎯 Chapter Objective

Is chapter me hum Image SEO ko detail me samjhenge. Aap seekhenge ki images ko SEO-friendly kaise banaya jata hai, image file names, ALT Text, image compression, modern image formats aur Google Image Search ke liye optimization kaise ki jati hai.

---

# 10.1 What is Image SEO?

**Image SEO** ek process hai jisme website ki images ko optimize kiya jata hai taaki search engines unhe easily understand kar sake aur users ko fast loading experience mile.

Simple Words:

> **Image SEO = Images ko Google aur Users dono ke liye optimize karna.**

---

# 10.2 Why Image SEO is Important?

Images sirf design ke liye nahi hoti.

Proper optimization se:

* Website Fast Load Hoti Hai
* Google Images me Ranking Milti Hai
* Better User Experience
* Better Accessibility
* Better Core Web Vitals
* More Organic Traffic

---

# 10.3 How Google Understands Images?

Google image ko human ki tarah directly nahi samajhta.

Google mainly ye signals use karta hai:

* File Name
* ALT Text
* Surrounding Content
* Captions
* Structured Data
* Page Context

Isliye image optimization bahut important hai.

---

# 10.4 Image File Name

Bad Example:

```text
IMG_20250629.jpg
```

Good Example:

```text
fire-extinguisher-mumbai.jpg
```

Rules:

* Meaningful Name
* Lowercase Letters
* Hyphens (-)
* Keyword Included
* No Spaces
* No Random Numbers

---

# 10.5 ALT Text

ALT (Alternative Text) image ka description hota hai.

Google aur Screen Readers isi description ko use karte hain.

Example:

```text
ABC Fire Extinguisher installed in a commercial office in Mumbai.
```

Benefits:

* Better SEO
* Accessibility
* Image Search Ranking

---

# 10.6 Image Title

Image Title user ko hover karne par additional information de sakta hai.

Example:

```text
ABC Fire Extinguisher
```

Title optional hai, lekin ALT Text mandatory hona chahiye.

---

# 10.7 Image Caption

Caption image ke niche dikhne wala text hota hai.

Example:

> Installation of CO₂ Fire Extinguisher at a corporate office in Mumbai.

Caption user engagement improve karta hai.

---

# 10.8 Image Size

Large images website ko slow bana deti hain.

Recommended:

* Compress Images
* Resize Before Upload
* Avoid Oversized Dimensions

Example:

❌ 8 MB Image

↓

✅ 250 KB Optimized Image

---

# 10.9 Image Compression

Compression se image ka size kam hota hai bina noticeable quality loss ke.

Popular Tools:

* TinyPNG
* Squoosh
* ImageOptim

Benefits:

* Faster Loading
* Better SEO
* Lower Bandwidth Usage

---

# 10.10 Image Formats

## JPEG (.jpg)

Best for:

* Photos
* Product Images

---

## PNG (.png)

Best for:

* Logos
* Transparent Background

---

## WebP ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

Modern image format.

Benefits:

* Smaller File Size
* Better Quality
* Faster Loading

Recommended for most websites.

---

## SVG

Best for:

* Icons
* Logos
* Simple Graphics

---

# 10.11 Responsive Images

Different devices ke liye different image sizes use karo.

Benefits:

* Faster Mobile Loading
* Better Performance
* Better User Experience

---

# 10.12 Lazy Loading

Lazy Loading ka matlab hai images tab load hongi jab user un tak scroll karega.

Benefits:

* Faster Initial Load
* Better Core Web Vitals
* Lower Data Usage

---

# 10.13 Image Sitemap

Agar website me bahut images hain to Image Sitemap banana useful hota hai.

Benefits:

* Better Image Crawling
* Better Image Indexing
* Faster Discovery

---

# 10.14 Structured Data for Images

Schema Markup image ko additional context deta hai.

Examples:

* Product Image
* Article Image
* Organization Logo

Benefits:

* Rich Results
* Better Search Visibility

---

# 10.15 Original Images vs Stock Images

### Original Images

* Better Trust
* Unique Content
* Better Branding

### Stock Images

* Easy to Use
* Generic Appearance
* Less Unique

Recommendation:

Business website ke liye maximum original images use karo.

